{"tid":1323133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(沙田示威) 年輕人，雨傘不是這麽用的！","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:19:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc725c560d7a09a8641ebefd6c157e2243a06f21","tid":1323133,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0716/U647P22T1D774248F1DT20190716142203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22T1D774248F1DT20190716142203.jpg&h=b2517978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：環球時報<br />\n<br />\n上個周末，在香港上水和沙田兩地，暴徒們又&ldquo;暴走&rdquo;了，他們連續兩天發起暴力衝擊，雨傘等物在他們手中成了&ldquo;致命兇器&rdquo;，紛紛砸向落單的警察，其瘋狂已經到了&ldquo;失去常性&rdquo;的程度。<br />\n<br />\n  在暴徒手中，雨傘都可以如此&ldquo;暴力&rdquo;。7月13日，香港上水。多名暴徒手持雨傘襲警，警察被打到跪倒在地，暴徒仍不罷手，地上散落一地破雨傘。這兇殘的一幕，被在場記者拍下，永遠定格：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141806.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141806.jpg&h=de8a22f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：環球時報<br />\n<br />\n7月14日，香港沙田，新城市廣場一處電梯旁。數十暴徒&ldquo;下死手&rdquo;圍毆一名警察。有人高喊&ldquo;別打了，別打了，別打了，再打會死人的！&rdquo;並衝上前用身體護住受傷警察。此時，這名警察已倒地不起：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141837.jpg&h=2bad1ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：香港商報<br />\n<br />\n7月14日，香港沙田，新城市廣場內。多名防爆警察被圍，暴徒不斷將雨傘、雜物擲向警察：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141851.jpg&h=9ed86ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：香港大公網<br />\n<br />\n7月14日，香港沙田，新城市廣場內。有警察被多名暴徒圍毆，有暴徒揪起警察頭部，讓同黨以雨傘施暴：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141904.jpg&h=736d4eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：大公網圖片<br />\n<br />\n7月14日，香港沙田，新城市廣場內。一名暴徒用鉗子鉗斷了一名警察的手指，而另一名警察的手指被暴徒咬斷。行兇之後，暴徒迅速作鳥獸散，現場留下兩把破傘，一灘血漬：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141928.jpg&h=0a347379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：&ldquo;警魂&rdquo;公眾號<br />\n<br />\n香港警方表示，暴力衝擊中，至少有十名警察受傷：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716141940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716141940.jpg&h=aacb1146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：香港大公網<br />\n<br />\n被暴徒鉗斷手指的警察同時後腦被打至腦出血：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716142004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716142004.jpg&h=169a037b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源： &ldquo;警魂&rdquo;公眾號<br />\n<br />\n香港警察臉書專頁曬出多張警察受傷照片，身上這些圓圓的紅印子，相信就是暴徒用雨傘戳傷的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716142020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716142020.jpg&h=bc262507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014年，有外媒曾把當時的香港&ldquo;占中&rdquo;事件浪漫化為&ldquo;雨傘革命&rdquo;，那麽這次，他們又將如何美化？不過，無論如何美化也洗不掉暴力行為的違法內涵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716142040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716142040.jpg&h=cf3c5c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而且，雨傘根本就不是這麽用的，也不應該這麽用，好嗎！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0716/774248.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"67f04f8bb30305d73d281afc641fc964517e7977","tid":1323133,"uid":156936,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都未打死, 往死裡打</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"531edf180b9a0252ec9e58acda9b5cfa38eb2237","tid":1323133,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:54.000Z","msg":"睇李連杰做黃飛鴻，佢通常係用遮柄打人<br />\n或者用嚟篤要害<br />\n班暴徒想攞彩扮黃飛鴻學啲唔學啲<br />\n搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec67ad886f89634ae08eccbc257d35a7d2540e8a","tid":1323133,"uid":51057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"我都覺得雨傘唔係咁用, 揮劈太低攻, 應該用黎刺擊"},{"pid":"ba2e4d87620ebe81bc3c1aae80c8d351a82a03e9","tid":1323133,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"警察不是這麼執法的！"},{"pid":"0f16012b8a7f338aea315d8ae50ac0d9369215c9","tid":1323133,"uid":247454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f716ea344cf99cd8f364c7a2453cc724844fbf36","tid":1323133,"uid":262674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"旁人勿說三道四，干預別家內政。環球切勿沉醉於帝國主義的家長式管治，妄想自己對香港有話語權，監察權。"},{"pid":"86ee7b77d7b075084d794ca0e6e7d1bb20409681","tid":1323133,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2g8pfbj/66os0000q7699oso1256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2g8pfbj%2F66os0000q7699oso1256.jpg&h=a32a3805&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"987fe3207a5035122d4a7f9bd7962d93394ba35d","tid":1323133,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被暴徒鉗斷手指的警察同時後腦被打至腦出血：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716142004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716142004.jpg&h=14e1b332&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38224cd3226003b6f69c1baa348e11fccb878059","tid":1323133,"uid":125021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"987fe3207a5035122d4a7f9bd7962d93394ba35d","tid":1323133,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被暴徒鉗斷手指的警察同時後腦被打至腦出血：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0716/U647P22DT20190716142004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0716%2FU647P22DT20190716142004.jpg&h=14e1b332&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"我都笑左 有鉗不如直接打落去"},{"pid":"6dcf0c2a9c4d8c0e66ada75b3e75a9761a635377","tid":1323133,"uid":277712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"外國特務片都有教 雨傘用嚟自衛🤙🏻<br />\n人不犯我 我不犯人"}]}